{{advert|date=October 2012}} {{unreferenced|date=October 2012}} {{Infobox Newspaper |name = Tripoli Post |image = |type = Weekly newspaper |format = [[Broadsheet]] |foundation = {{start date and age|1999}} |owners = |headquarters =[[Tripoli Tower]], [[Tripoli]] |editor = |website = |ISSN= }}
The '''''Tripoli Post''''' was a newspaper that first appeared in 1999. Its objective was to communicate Libya’s news and views to the rest of the world.
The Tripoli Post and The Tripoli Post Online had focused on serving readers by making information available with regard to Libya’s politics, business, culture, sports, history and the country’s dynamic growing population. This was in addition to covering world events.
